american-adventure.name: The American Adventure
american-adventure.what_it_is: Patriotic mixed-media and audio-animatronic theater presentation on U.S. history
american-adventure.summary: Audio-Animatronics, film and music bring America's past to life during this 30-minute show at the American Adventure Pavilion.

alberta-bound.name: Alberta Bound
alberta-bound.summary: Canadian folk band that plays on the Mill Stage in Epcot's Canada Pavilion.

the-british-revolution.name: British Revolution
the-british-revolution.summary: Bang your head to the best of British rock as this 4-piece band plays everything from psychedelic to punk.

agent-ps-world-showcase-adventure.name: Agent P's World Showcase Adventure
agent-ps-world-showcase-adventure.what_it_is: Interactive scavenger hunt in select World Showcase pavillions
agent-ps-world-showcase-adventure.ultimate_task: Complete mission in 1 country as core. Each additional country counts as bonus.
agent-ps-world-showcase-adventure.summary: Thwart the diabolical Dr. Doofenshmirtz during a sleuth-worthy scavenger hunt around the World Showcase!

serveur-amusant.name: Serveur Amusant
serveur-amusant.summary: These French acrobats enthrall audiences with their astonishing acts of balance and coordination. C’est magnifique!

jeweled-dragon-acrobats.name: The Jeweled Dragon Acrobats
jeweled-dragon-acrobats.summary: This vibrant acrobatic troupe from China performs breathtaking feats of strength, agility and balance.

gran-fiesta-tour-starring-the-three-caba.name: Gran Fiesta Tour Starring The Three Caballeros
gran-fiesta-tour-starring-the-three-caba.sort_name: gran fiesta tour starring the three caballeros
gran-fiesta-tour-starring-the-three-caba.summary: Take in the sights of Mexico and the antics of the 3 feathered amigos on this gentle boat ride through the Mexico Pavilion.

seas-with-nemo-friends.name: The Seas with Nemo & Friends
seas-with-nemo-friends.what_it_is: Ride through a tunnel in The Seas' main tank
seas-with-nemo-friends.summary: Go under the sea—without getting wet—on this attraction based on Disney•Pixar's Finding Nemo which finds Nemo lost again.

jammitors.name: JAMMitors
jammitors.summary: This clean-up crew breaks it down as they drum with some unlikely utensils!

matsuriza.name: Matsuriza
matsuriza.summary: Experience the thundering sound of Taiko, a time-honored form of drumming—at the Japan Pavilion at Epcot.

reflections-of-china.name: Reflections of China
reflections-of-china.what_it_is: Film about the Chinese people and culture
reflections-of-china.summary: Journey through ancient and modern China while watching this 14-minute Circle-Vision 360° film, screening in the China Pavilion.

movie-preview.name: Disney & Pixar Short Film Festival
movie-preview.summary: Experience popular Disney and Pixar short films like never before—in 4D for the first time ever.

beauty-beast-sing-along.name: Beauty and the Beast Sing-Along
beauty-beast-sing-along.what_it_is: Small film re-telling of the movie, with audience singing

rose-crown-pub-musician.name: Rose & Crown Pub Musician
rose-crown-pub-musician.summary: Pop inside this boisterous British pub for a bit of brilliant entertainment—performed live by our own resident musician. Grab a pint and share a toast as you sing along to smashing tunes from pubs all around the United Kingdom!

test-track.name: Test Track
test-track.when_to_go: The first 30 minutes the park is open, just before closing, or use FastPass+.
test-track.summary: Design a virtual concept vehicle and then go for a high-octane spin at this attraction that’s thrilling and creative.

epcot-forever.name: Epcot Forever
epcot-forever.what_it_is: Night Spectacular with Lasers, Fireworks, and Kites

mission-space-green.name: Mission: SPACE Green
mission-space-green.when_to_go: First or last hour park is open, or use Fastpass
mission-space-green.special_needs: May cause motion sickness. Please see Cast Member at the attraction for further cautionary information.
mission-space-green.ultimate_task: Ride either orange or green. No bonus for riding both.
mission-space-green.summary: Experience authentic NASA-style training on a thrilling ride to Mars—or orbit around Earth during an all-new, family-friendly mission.

mission-space-orange.name: Mission: SPACE Orange
mission-space-orange.when_to_go: First or last hour park is open, or use Fastpass
mission-space-orange.special_needs: May cause motion sickness. Please see Cast Member at the attraction for further cautionary information.
mission-space-orange.ultimate_task: Ride either orange or green. No bonus for riding both.
mission-space-orange.summary: Experience authentic NASA-style training on a thrilling ride to Mars—or orbit around Earth during an all-new, family-friendly mission.

the-seas-main-tank-and-exhibits.name: The Seas Main Tank and Exhibits
the-seas-main-tank-and-exhibits.what_it_is: A huge saltwater aquarium, plus exhibits on oceanography, ocean ecology, and sea life

matboukha-groove.name: Matboukha Groove
matboukha-groove.summary: Sway along to a unique fusion of tunes influenced by a variety of world styles.

spaceship-earth.name: Spaceship Earth
spaceship-earth.what_it_is: Educational dark ride through past, present, and future
spaceship-earth.summary: Travel in time and explore the history of communication on a ride that takes you from the Stone Age to the computer age.

frozen-ever-after.name: Frozen Ever After
frozen-ever-after.when_to_go: Before noon., after 7 p.m., or use FastPass+
frozen-ever-after.summary: Hoist the sails in Arendelle aboard an ancient Norwegian vessel as you set out into the wondrous wintery world of Frozen!

candlelight-processional.name: Candlelight Processional
candlelight-processional.ultimate_task: View full show. Standing behind seating area is acceptable.

sergio.name: Sergio
sergio.summary: Laugh with master juggler and mime Sergio as he engages you in a lighthearted, old Italian piazza-style juggling show.

walt-disney-imagineering-presents-epcot-.name: Walt Disney Imagineering presents the Epcot Experience
walt-disney-imagineering-presents-epcot-.sort_name: walt disney imagineering presents the epcot experience

voices-of-liberty.name: Voices of Liberty
voices-of-liberty.summary: Gather ‘round this outstanding a cappella group as they bring patriotic music to life beneath an acoustically perfect dome.

margret-almer-bavarian-band.name: Margret Almer & The Bavarian Band
margret-almer-bavarian-band.summary: Live yodeling and German music. This show is part of the Epcot International Festival of the Holidays.

royal-sommerhus.name: Meet Anna and Elsa at Royal Sommerhus
royal-sommerhus.what_it_is: Meet and greet with the Frozen princesses
royal-sommerhus.sort_name: meet anna and elsa at royal sommerhus
royal-sommerhus.summary: Chill out with Frozen royalty, Anna & Elsa, and enjoy an enchanted Character Greeting in their new summer home.

guardians-galaxy-awesome-mix-live.name: The Guardians of the Galaxy – Awesome Mix Live!
guardians-galaxy-awesome-mix-live.sort_name: guardians of galaxy awesome mix live

living-with-the-land.name: Living with the Land
living-with-the-land.what_it_is: Indoor boat-ride adventure chronicling the past, present, and future of farming and agriculture in the United States
living-with-the-land.when_to_go: Before 10:30 a.m. or after 5 p.m., or use Fastpass if available
living-with-the-land.summary: Sail through the greenhouses of The Land Pavilion on a boat tour and behold 9-pound lemons, Mickey-shaped pumpkins and more!

canada-far-wide-in-circle-vision-360.name: Canada Far and Wide in Circle-Vision 360
canada-far-wide-in-circle-vision-360.sort_name: canada far and wide in circlevision 360

soarin.name: Soarin'
soarin.when_to_go: First 30 minutes the park is open or use Fastpass
soarin.summary: Take flight on a breezy, airborne adventure as you hang glide above some of the most breathtaking wonders the world has to offer.

disney-on-broadway-concert.name: Disney on Broadway Concert Series
disney-on-broadway-concert.summary: This concert series-- part of the Epcot International Festival of the Arts--will showcase all the Disney musical hits live

journey-into-imagination-with-figment.name: Journey Into Imagination With Figment
journey-into-imagination-with-figment.summary: Figment the playful, purple dragon is your guide on this whimsical ride through the Imagination Institute.

mariachi-cobre.name: Mariachi Cobre
mariachi-cobre.summary: This spirited mariachi band performs the traditional folk music of Jalisco, Mexico, throughout the Mexico Pavilion.

musique-aramenco.name: Musique Aramenco
musique-aramenco.summary: Musique Aramenco performs with a fusion of traditional and popular dance music from the Southern Mediterranean and Northern Africa. Shows include the darbuka drum, violins, and a belly dancer. This show is part of the Epcot International Festival of the Holidays.

turtle-talk-with-crush.name: Turtle Talk with Crush
turtle-talk-with-crush.summary: Gather ’round a window to the ocean for a real-time Q-and-A session with your favorite totally tubular turtle. Righteous!

impressions-de-france.name: Impressions de France
impressions-de-france.what_it_is: Film essay on the French people and country
impressions-de-france.summary: Enjoy this 18-minute film showcasing the grandeur, charm and romance of one of Europe’s most enchanting countries.

mariachi-cobre-presents-story-coco.name: Mariachi Cobre Presents... The Story of Coco
mariachi-cobre-presents-story-coco.ultimate_task: Watch this or another live Mexico music show for 5 minutes.
mariachi-cobre-presents-story-coco.sort_name: mariachi cobre presents the story of coco
mariachi-cobre-presents-story-coco.summary: The immensely talented musicians of Mariachi Cobre are joined by a pair of Folklórico dancers to tell the tale of Miguel Rivera, his love of music, and his journey to find what matters most – his familia.

awesome-planet.name: Awesome Planet
awesome-planet.what_it_is: Film presentation on the Earth's animals and landscapes
awesome-planet.summary: this all-new film uses in-theater effects (including wind, scents and water) to tell the story of life on our planet and why it’s vitally important to care for it.

mischievous-magical-barn-santa-in-norway.name: A Mischievous, Magical Barn Santa in Norway
mischievous-magical-barn-santa-in-norway.summary: Sigrid, a Norwegian farm girl Sigrid, shares her holiday experiences related to a tricky Barn Santa.
